1. Download and install Anki's latest version from their official website: https://apps.ankiweb.net/

2. Login to your account and Sync everything

3. Download and install "AnKing Master v8.apkg" from https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1P5mvoCBO_xy3Dqx1w1GYbBYjpyy_yPjM
It should also be in the same folder/directory as this txt file. Just double-click on it when it's downloaded

4. Add all the Add-ons. Instructions provided in another txt file in this file's folder/directory.
